channel.name: From Excel Exporter
channel.description:
This channel will serve up an Excel spread sheet which has a button that can be used send the data in an Excel table into Iguana.
This web service takes that data and turns each row into a JSON object which is then pushed into the queue.
See: http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/excel-exporter
Use this channel with the From Excel Exporter.
